<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Hospital</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #444;
        }

        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .services {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .services button {
            display: block;
            width: 80%;
            margin: 10px auto;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .services button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .footer-text {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Hospital</h1>
        <p>Thank you for choosing our hospital for your healthcare needs.</p>
        <p>Here, we strive to provide the highest quality medical care to our patients.</p>
        <p>Learn more about our services and specialties:</p>
        <div class="services">
            <button>Internal Medicine</button>
            <button>Pediatrics</button>
            <button>Surgery</button>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-text">If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>